 seeker. \\n \\n \\n \\nComplete set of seven class recordings available as video and audio mp3, together with six guided meditations available in mp3 format \\n \\nThis complete retreat package includes: \\n \\n Over 8 Hours of Video and Audio Content \\n 6 Powerful Guided Meditations \\n 3 Midday Seminars and 4 Evening Satsangs \\n 6 Question and Answer Sessions with Shunyamurti \\n \\n \\n \\nTable of Contents of this Retreat: \\n \\n Session 1 – You've Been Badly Framed--Or So You Believe! [1:16:30] \\n Session 2 – The Seven Elements of Grace [1:05:59] \\n Session 3 – Principles of the Yoga of the Unattainable [1:12:58] \\n Session 4 – The Holographic Theory of Christ--and All of Us [1:13:11] \\n Session 5 – The Final Phase of Self-Realization: The Ordinary [1:09:28] \\n Session 6 – Choose Wholeness or Ongoing Fragmentation [1:05:19] \\n Session 7 – The Secret Sameness of Delusion and Enlightenment [1:18:17] \\n \\n \\n \\nAny issues, questions or comments? Please email us - store@satyoga.org	PHYSICAL	125.00	125.00	\N	\N	\N	https://www.satyoga.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/April-2025-Product-Square.png	["https://www.satyoga.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/April-2025-Product-Square.png"]		["simple", "downloadable", "virtual"]	[{"id": "7448c1a6-267d-4608-9ad7-9f5b405f0d07", "name": "You've Been Framed Audio-Video Package", "url": "https://www.satyoga.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Youve-Been-Framed-Audio-Video-Package.pdf"}]	["Featured", "Retreat Packages"]	[]	{"youtube": [], "vimeo": [], "cloudflare": ["https://iframe.videodelivery.net/042c89cbe05ef74ab7eebdaf37291f05", "https://iframe.videodelivery.net/2e542a8bfb8ed208834a27f1a08cc6f6", "https://iframe.videodelivery.net/5860a47f1c5440d645371566855975b5", "https://iframe.videodelivery.net/a2e22cc4dc074d255a15dee4cffe6b17", "https://iframe.videodelivery.net/cd7843a6f056d736d4badd013b05f354", "https://iframe.videodelivery.net/d70e7b1e9dd6b597e74637cd23549bf9", "https://iframe.videodelivery.net/e14098a3d5a62b1de217f