1835ab75-aa85-4d8f-9491-9897c2c9b660	why-our-situation-is-hopeless-yet-hilarious	Why Our Situation is Hopeless, Yet Hilarious!	Complete Audio-Video Retreat Teachings Package \\nAfter purchase, you will receive a PDF guide that includes the link and password to the retreat website, where you will be able to watch all the classes and listen to and download the audio. \\n	Why Our Situation is Hopeless, Yet Hilarious! \\n \\n \\nThis momentous seminar is a powerful sacred ritual. It begins with a deep exploration of how and why human civilization is now being destroyed. We learn that the world’s wounds start from within our own divided consciousness. We are then introduced to a new understanding of our suffering, based on a profound concept called the Attis Complex, based on the ancient myth of Attis and Cybele. \\n \\nOur rite of passage, guided by Shunyamurti, then helps us undo our unfortunate collective repression of death, which is behind the return of the repressed as a global death drive. The journey takes us to an extraordinary interpretation of the famous Cheshire Cat, which explains why we are so embedded in delusion and think it is normal. There is no greater gift than receiving a God’s-eye-view of this dying dream field—even though the full Presence of God is intolerable to the ego, which would instantly dissolve if it starts to resonate with that supreme vibrational frequency. \\n \\nIn Act Two of the retreat, we learn The Art of the Ordeal. We must come to terms with the suffering that has become an inevitable part of life, and more importantly, we learn how to overcome it. Here it is the Osiris Complex that comes to our aid. The journey then takes us into the heart of quantum physics, and the rude awakening that science has brought to us: that the world is unreal. Not only is matter a fictional category, but both space and time are illusory. The spiritual significance of all this is immense. The teaching concludes with a convergence of science with postmodern philosophy, ancient tribal wisdom, and the Eastern teachings of nonduality. \\n \\nIn the final act of our sacred gathering, we learn how to leapfrog all our existential ordeals, and immediately transport our souls into the blissful light of eternal Presence. This can be achieved through reason alone, if our minds are coherent enough, but our chances greatly improve if our hearts are open and there is love for the Infinite Intelligence from Whom we derive our Being. If you take in these teachings and reflect on them seriously, that is all you need to attain Liberation in Life. \\n \\n \\n \\nComplete set of seven class recordings available as video and audio mp3, together with six guided meditations available in mp3 format \\n \\nThis complete retreat package includes: \\n \\n Over 4 Hours of Video and Audio Content \\n 3 Powerful Guided Meditations \\n 1 Midday Seminars and 2 Evening Satsangs \\n 3 Question and Answer Sessions with Shunyamurti \\n \\n \\n \\nTable of Contents of this Retreat: \\n \\n Session 1 – The Rite of Passage: From Hopeless to Hilarious [1:12:13] \\n Session 2 – The Art of the Ordeal [1:07:48] \\n Session 3 – There is No Ordeal in the Real [1:15:51] \\n \\n \\n \\nAny issues, questions or comments? Please email us - store@satyoga.org	PHYSICAL	95.00	95.00	\N	\N	\N	https://www.satyoga.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/July-2025-Store-Product.png	["https://www.satyoga.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/July-2025-Store-Product.png"]		["simple", "downloadable", "virtual"]	[{"id": "22da6b79-c41a-4cb1-8849-1277dda7410e", "name": "Why Our Situation is Hopeless, Yet Hilarious! AV Package", "url": "https://www.satyoga.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Why-Our-Situation-is-Hopeless-Yet-Hilarious-Audio-Video-Package.pdf"}]	["Featured", "Retreat Packages"]	[]	{"youtube": [], "vimeo": [], "cloudflare": [], "mp4": [], "mp3": ["https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/4f9xpwypwun6vrud/250704_Hopeless_Hilarious_Evening_GM_Teaching_Q_A85elk.mp3", "https://mcdn.podbean.com/m