043a9b88-1c7f-4551-8bbd-d91faa9b3a54	12-12-12	12.12.12	This day has great symbolic significance. The number 12 signifies completion, wholeness, and fulfillment of one’s Godly mission. One can think of such examples as the twelve months of the year and the twelve houses of the zodiac, the twelve tribes of Israel, the twelve labors of Hercules. This number is occurring now in such an intensified form (on 12/12/12) because it is the time of completion on three different levels: the planetary level, the individual egoic level, and the spiritual level, the latter meaning the relationship of the soul to God.	video	gyani	0	\N	\N	\N	https://www.members.satyoga.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2020/05/3.jpg	\N	2019-06-30 22:51:55	video_teaching	\N	0	2025-10-28 15:31:23.835527	2025-10-28 15:31:23.835527	[]	[]	[]	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	[]
